1
00:00:01,640 --> 00:00:04,600
[female]庄贤惠:
你胡说八道什么呀我可什么事都没让你干
What nonsense are you talking about? I didn't ask you to do anything.

2
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:06,540
[female]庄贤惠:
别赖在我头上
Don't pin this on me.

3
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:08,480
[male]男员工:
都是你毁了我
You ruined me.

4
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:09,280
[male]男员工:
都是你一都是你
It was all you! All you!

5
00:00:09,280 --> 00:00:09,960
[female]庄贤惠:
你要干什么别过来
What are you doing? Stay away!

6
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:11,280
[male]男员工:
你不仁就别怪我不义
If you're unfair, don't blame me for being ruthless.

7
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:12,720
[female]庄贤惠:
滚开滚开
Get off me! Get off me!

8
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:14,220
[male]黑衣男子:
把他给我拉开
Pull him away from her.

9
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:18,160
[male]董事长:
我的办公室不是让你们撒泼的
My office is not a place for you to make a scene.

10
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:22,240
[male]男员工:
董事长求求你再给我一次机会
Chairman, I'm begging you, give me another chance.

11
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:24,400
[male]男员工:
我还有几百万的房贷没有还
I still have a mortgage of millions to pay off.

12
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:26,280
[male]男员工:
我不能失去这份工作
I can't lose this job.

13
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:28,040
[male]董事长:
你不能失去这份工作
You can't lose this job?

14
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:31,040
[male]董事长:
要不是我夫人多才多艺
If it weren't for my multi-talented wife

15
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:35,560
[male]董事长:
霍氏这些重要合作商都被你们得罪光了
You've offended all of Huo's key business partners!

16
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:38,880
[male]董事长:
到时候就会有成百上千的员工
Then, hundreds, even thousands of employees

17
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,800
[male]董事长:
因为你失去工作而流离失所
will lose their jobs and homes because of you.

18
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,280
[male]董事长:
他们跟谁哭去
Who are they supposed to cry to?

19
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:48,520
[male]董事长:
跟错了主子做错事就要接受惩罚
You chose the wrong master. You did the wrong thing. Now, face the punishment.

20
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:50,840
[male]董事长:
收拾你的东西
Pack your things.

21
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,920
[male]董事长:
睡天桥去吧
Go sleep under a bridge.

22
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,920
[male]董事长:
我不想再看见你
I don't want to see you again.

23
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,560
[male]董事长:
带走
Take him away.

24
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:01,160
[male]男员工:
董事长我错了都是庄贤惠逼我干的
Chairman, I was wrong! Zhuang Xianhui made me do it!

25
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,320
[female]庄贤惠:
震东
Zhendong

26
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:05,840
[female]庄贤惠:
震东我真的不是故意的
Zhendong, I really didn't mean to.

27
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:06,920
[female]庄贤惠:
我知道错了
I know I was wrong.

